January
???



Welll that's a short summmary...through all  the times I cried this year to the times where I felt so high on life I wanna than kall of you because even if we don't talk anyomre you have taught me something about myself..THis year has been amazing I truly have discovered who I am...and I hope 2006 only brings more good times.

so now that Melissa has inspired me to write a brief entry..i never ever write long entries....so life has had major up's and down's the last month..i wont bore you with the details..i love that i use no punctutation while writing these entries..but neway grease is going very well we open in like a month..i love everything about it..the ppl..the show...the new friends i made..meliss whom i looove ...but neway on the down side of things i came home today to find no 1 in my house and then got a phone from my mom saying that my cuzin was in a motorcycle crsh...so since 2:30 my mom has been calling me updating me on his status....he just went in for surgery to see if they can salvage his leg....im praying for him...so that's a long enuff entry for me..later ppl

Ya kno whats realli wierd..is how im sitting here rite now instead of going downstairs..why u ask?....well my aunt lives downstairs and has company over rite now...not just any company but carol and jeff....carol is my aunts good friend and jeff is her son..ive known both since i was very young..me ,my cousin chris and jeff would always play together and jeff would treat me like a sis....but things change..i remember going to see him in the sound of music at his skoool...well sum 1 gave him flowers and he said they were too gurly..so he gave them to me and that moment has been forever stuck n my mind...since that happened 5 years ago ive only seen him mayb 4 times..o did i forget to mention jeff has cancer thats on and off again...and bc of this hes tried taking his life several times...i havent seen him in mayb 2 years...but rite now he's sitting
downstairs just feet away and im too scared to do nething about it.....mayb out of fear that my aunt will yell at me for intruding while she has company..or mayb im just scared bc wen i walk downstairs..he wont b sweet lil jeff nemore..wut i want more than nething is for him to b the same person..ive always had a crush on him and i wonder day after day if hes changed....rite now i have the opportunity to see if he has..but for sum reason i am just to nervous and scared to do it...mayb sum things r just better left alone?..or mayb not?
